(13,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/seating/seating-products/ava','https://www.instagram.com/p/C9Txn9WS708/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469583713_18314556817167794_6359852932275539533_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=106&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=FlKB0AJGCz8Q7kNvwEXLQBL&_nc_oc=AdqF_8xywKlryQUTjaiUn0E_y-7q3cp-Q9ALv1OHPuJIeLjOBeU6LauUCXtU6F2HgJg&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQDBJ4i7fQyIRkhz4Os0EydVBc3B4wrUJKIUndfhzTTqFg&oe=6A510A8C','Total Fitouts has transformed Fiorelli Packing’s office into a space that epitomises modern sophistication and functional elegance.  The design harmoniously blends natural wooden tones with sophisticated grey and black fabrics, punctuated by textured furnishings and lush greenery. For informal interactions or a relaxing coffee break, our plush Ava lounges paired with luxurious Oscar coffee tables create the perfect setting.  To see more of this project, visit Fiorelli Packing in Krost Projects linked in bio. 🔗  Builder: @TotalFitouts Photographer: @PixelCollective_Aus  Get in touch with us today:  🌐 www.krost.com.au  📞 1800 1KROST 📧 sales@krost.com.au  Visit one of our world-class showrooms: Sydney - 33 Ricketty Street, Mascot NSW, 2020 Melbourne - 617 Spencer St, West Melbourne VIC, 3003  . . . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostProjects #KrostBusinessFurniture #OfficeDesign #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialFurniture #CommercialDesign #Architecture #InspirationalWorkplaces #InteriorArchitecture #CommercialFitout #AustralianDesign #Corporate #OfficeFitout','C9Txn9WS708','Krost','IMAGE',7);
