(64,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/workstations/workstations-products/elki','https://www.instagram.com/p/DI-Q_e-S3Wk/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/491893753_18329743378167794_2872388197706764677_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=101&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=psr7-E-Kl4EQ7kNvwFf5io3&_nc_oc=Adqu53PYhS_tyKBccexYrzsjb1KEEWBWscVuSjQTlvU5W5X9XuJEuIjcpLEB_Qe5JEQ&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQDexkEIxfO1O1P4IOaTirpyl758opaC1isD8ikRWZZNpg&oe=6A511D63','Built with craftsmanship and intent, our Universal Locker with Planter introduces smart storage, bespoke finishes and a living layer of greenery into the workspace. Customisable in size, material and lock options, it offers a seamless balance of functionality and softness in design, creating a setting that feels both tailored and connected to its environment.  See more of the new product range in our 2025 Catalogue out now.  🔗 Click the link in our bio to view it online or order your free copy now!  #Krost #2025Catalogue #Krost2025Collection #Officefurniture #KrostBusinessFurniture #furnitureshowroom #officeworkstations #officedesign #joinery #lockers #customjoinery','DI-Q_e-S3Wk','Krost','IMAGE',0),
