(138,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/accessories/accessories-products/Monitor-Arms','https://www.instagram.com/p/C5PoImXvR-q/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469480354_18314547373167794_5088938687851564920_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=102&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=D4OyxvmNnxYQ7kNvwE1Eb9k&_nc_oc=Adr8mhS-A2m7-mSin8YcHshSUi08pfABqfxRpVnFYOGOMlmlWaLcefCXjk-31FLVfmg&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=RPLiYzAUeNt_Ca2YdP1m7A&oh=00_AQBhffpE4gijmQeg4ZzmtULnLsMagz1JPB8gfQuwMFA7FA&oe=6A508408','Vemi have designed an office space that balances modern business needs with design-forward thinking.  Our Benchwork workstations promote teamwork with Arc screens for privacy and clear communication. Our Arlo chairs offer a casual spot for collaboration or quiet reflection while our Universal lockers keep this open office space organised.   Designer: @vemi.au  .  .  . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostBusinessFurniture #KrostProjects #OfficeDesign #OpenOffice #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialDesign #CommercialFitout #Lockers #Collaboration','C5PoImXvR-q','Krost','IMAGE',3),
(138,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/accessories/accessories-products/Monitor-Arms','https://www.instagram.com/p/CqJKpvesFZf/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/655067667_18101660548926835_6087091408812613513_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=106&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=nroloxyYqVwQ7kNvwGor9jL&_nc_oc=AdqqOG9yzveLfIqV0lS3d-dGN1aBHLsmN0-Znv-yYHG5QvYskMsJn9Bd51T7xYjHaeQ&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=RPLiYzAUeNt_Ca2YdP1m7A&oh=00_AQBTV6Sl8ZlR9uLqpfzxW-e0PhtZqHJlS1bS-yYXO12lnA&oe=6A5074B4','Bringing the Buzz to the office with our new range of workstations and tables. Designed in-house and locally made in our Sydney manufacturing facilities, the panel design is made of a recyclable honeycomb core that is lightweight and durable. ⁠ Made from 43% recycled material and 23% by-products from the sawmill industry, it s not only a sustainable choice, but also a stylish and functional addition for any contemporary office. Buzz is available in four modern woodgrain finishes and a premium black or white satin finish with anti-fingerprint properties. ⁠ Enquire today⁠ .⁠ .⁠ .⁠ .⁠ #krost #krostfurniture #krostbusinessfurniture #krost2023catalogue #krost2023 #krost2023collection #office furniture #commercialfurniture #workstations #officedesign #officefurnituretrends #commercialdesign #commercialfitout #officeinteriors #desk #meetingtable #boardroomtable #buzz','CqJKpvesFZf','krost','IMAGE',4),
(138,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/accessories/accessories-products/Monitor-Arms','https://www.instagram.com/p/CE0bkV0FFVh/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/615335112_18055351076378091_1746039718086397062_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=5E9ZIs1vlncQ7kNvwHWBHaJ&_nc_oc=AdpriFUt6fBkP9wTtQ1rYONTQxdw8EwdDDZPmSS_Z8fWJgdhzgCOEUYbA2VLTwcneXg&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=L5Ltoxshc5ZJJnFWKEbCvQ&oh=00_AQDuHZ0oHIHqZkLwZ5_Rb1Y4-4cgh_44gZM38DYJstqctw&oe=6A506CB3','Our Trak screen range has been extended and has welcomed clear Perspex panels to the family. Available in multiple widths and two heights (400 & 600mm), these Perspex screens are impermeable, easily cleanable and create a physical barrier between employees. If your office is already fitted with our Trak rails and you would like to update your screens, talk to our team and they’ll happily assist . . . . #krost #krostfurniture #krostbusinessfurniture #officefurniture #officescreens #commercialfurniture #commercialfitout #perspexscreens #officeinspiration #officesnapshots #covidsafe #covid19 #safework #safeworkplace #worksafe #covidprotection #trak #sneezeguard #deskscreen','CE0bkV0FFVh','krost','IMAGE',5),
