(156,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/tables/tables-products/monolite-counter-table','https://www.instagram.com/p/C9_2krxSwTN/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469591968_18314557090167794_8875059087578685796_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=pWSrtUjNwiUQ7kNvwHHja4j&_nc_oc=AdqsnjmBH14Rmkrj4AqGf1u8L1ZwICCa0mwe3fGc4UDhyidGoqtr7Wt05jwwBcNUixY&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQBwzy6eGvRAYricjdpEJKkLl1ihd5FpUAUCNF0c_VHz5w&oe=6A510A06','Monolite is a contemporary table range designed by Boris Berlin, defined by its distinctive thick tubular leg detail.  Inspired by monoliths and slab-like sculptures, Monolite’s design embodies simplicity as its core aesthetic principle.  Featuring locally manufactured worktops, Monolite can be customised to any size, making it ideal for a wide range of commercial settings and applications. Its design ensures exceptional structural integrity.  Visit one of our world-class showrooms and see our craftsmanship up close: Sydney | 33 Ricketty Street, Mascot NSW, 2020 Melbourne | 617 Spencer St, West Melbourne VIC, 3003  Get in touch with us today:  🌐 www.krost.com.au  📞 1800 1KROST 📧 sales@krost.com.au  Photography | @PixelCollective_Aus   . . . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostProjects #KrostBusinessFurniture #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialFurniture #CommercialDesign #InspirationalWorkplaces #FurnitureShowroom #VisitUs #CommercialFitout #AustralianDesign #OfficeFitout #QualityService #Monolite #BorisBerlin','C9_2krxSwTN','Krost','IMAGE',0),
(157,'https://krost.com.au/products/meeting-tables/monolite-table','https://www.instagram.com/p/DaRuQd8v5LC/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/731614913_18383359825167794_8419416900484595075_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=108&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=dptqJ2Z230IQ7kNvwHUrThR&_nc_oc=Adrq3XeI51TPe6RudEoUtJEs2ZdNwb4VpLoQ-9CZhBbstcOa8Yfh-PPnLw5-wruxdlg&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQAClNfFprcjqmaa000i1WdsdxNoCgucfg8UQpDGCkdy0w&oe=6A50F0E6','A monolith, lightened.   That was the brief Boris Berlin set himself, and Monolite is the answer. The range is built around a single engineering move, an oversized steel saddle plate that lets the top span without a frame underneath.  Substantial in presence. Restrained in line. One quiet object, across meeting, breakroom and counter settings.  🔗 Read the full story on our blog via the link on bio.   #BorisBerlin #MonoliteTable #DesignerFurniture #CommercialInteriors #OfficeFurniture Krost','DaRuQd8v5LC','BorisBerlin','IMAGE',0),
