(160,'https://krost.com.au/products/occasional-seating/noa','https://www.instagram.com/p/DVz6OcCjyOd/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/650847001_18368127472167794_5547799131184722595_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=111&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=gL8MdNLdkQMQ7kNvwGJFfkA&_nc_oc=AdqqjgTtEH4mqfK6cr7cVlXblKpXZJaNEA_EVFRhmXmTtUje_aX56fnhqYxcK7Zuwqc&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQCqQsoXYAQM6pdpQ-aro5ZtpBJEnWG4o7CQcN0FT7Jvmg&oe=6A510E79','Brisbane, we’ve officially arrived! 💯   Our new home on Stanley Street is now open, and it’s a milestone we’re incredibly proud of. We’ve designed the space to reflect Krost modern philosophy, merging refined aesthetics and tactile materiality with our latest 2026 Collection in a curated environment.   A gallery for inspiration and contemporary space creation. Now ready to explore at 936 Stanley St E, East Brisbane.  Photo | Edt Photography  Get in touch with our Brisbane team today: 🌐 www.krost.com.au 📞 1800 1KROST  Marketa Vrbatova  📧 marketa@krost.com.au  #krost #officefurniture #showroom #brisbane #commercialfurniture','DVz6OcCjyOd','krost','IMAGE',0),
(162,'https://krost.com.au/products/task-seating/ohvi','https://www.instagram.com/p/DPS5WBEjjlY/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/558417364_18346107067167794_677605259095809252_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=9KChrx_7pGIQ7kNvwE9Thnh&_nc_oc=AdrQy4qcDIGLXFYEiEQSy08fk2pS9i5UDmcnLzp2uFF0pV4JSI2stc5A_ELah0QOd44&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQBDCg9lveraZGZyW0I44sYakaVh9IC4DTSPRqoZq4SdVQ&oe=6A50F612','Featuring in @indesignlive, our new Ace height-adjustable system is engineered for design-led workspaces with the world’s thinnest column profile.   It is a new standard for the modern office, where adaptability, ergonomics, and design come together to create better ways of working.  🔗 Visit the article linked in our bio to discover our story of Ace.   📍 Visit one of our world-class showrooms: Sydney | 33 Ricketty Street, Mascot NSW, 2020 Melbourne | 617 Spencer St, West Melbourne VIC, 3003  Get in touch with us today: 🌐 www.krost.com.au 📞 1800 1KROST 📧 sales@krost.com.au  #Krost #Officefurniture #Officedesign #ModernWorkspace #CollaborativeSpaces #CommercialFitout #Ace #Workstations #SittoStand #HeightAdjustableworkstations #thinnest #legprofile #officeaesthetics','DPS5WBEjjlY','Krost','IMAGE',0),
(162,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/seating/seating-products/ohvi','https://www.instagram.com/p/DIiIMJLSv7j/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/490059695_18328673686167794_2801744441298869332_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=104&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=4Li4oVWCfgkQ7kNvwGI_rqm&_nc_oc=Adq-V3MCeHDyZO7haWda-TtVxRDUMEnDODFwxRRT_eU5FzL_903C7LclmqJAYqaFDYs&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQAuP9pDWzpFDps6tvwztkqukpOWn1U37GKL-uYN7koPGQ&oe=6A50FACF','Ohvi.   Defined with a sense of ease, Ohvi’s continuous curved back introduces a softer, more sculptural approach to task seating. The fluid form wraps around its breathable mesh back, bringing visual lightness and a modern minimalist expression to the workspace. With discreet adjustments and ergonomic support built into its clean lines, Ohvi delivers a quiet confidence that enhances focus without distraction.  See more of the new product range in our 2025 Catalogue out now.  🔗 Click the link in our bio to view it online or order your free copy now!  #Krost #2025Catalogue #Krost2025Collection #Officefurniture #KrostBusinessFurniture #furnitureshowroom #officedesign #workstations #officechairs #ohvi #ergonomic','DIiIMJLSv7j','Krost','IMAGE',1),
