(225,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/seating/seating-products/ted-stool','https://www.instagram.com/p/DCYYrojy7Rv/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/466996364_18311990647167794_7015525670598381068_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=105&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=sod8IB5nJIoQ7kNvwEROXvQ&_nc_oc=AdoFKgORlGr14RhRD077vxqWUaNcx25vWMCmSf3mi145ANfpEAhc-yC6EHdOds8vUY4&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQDboVJhFrH54U83vGqa7y47hmgarOooqdInkhHRNTdPyQ&oe=6A511791','Whether it’s an impromptu brainstorming session, a quick coffee break, or a formal team meeting, our Co-op Counter Table paired with our Ted Stools create the perfect setting.   Our Co-op counter table supports collaborative interaction. seamlessly blending into any office setting with its round stainless steel base, available in black or white textured powder coat.  With its soft curves and contoured back, the Ted stool offers aesthetic appeal and comfort from every angle, combining a sleek plywood seat with solid ash timber.  Builder | @hasbuilt_projects  Visit one of our world-class showrooms: Sydney | 33 Ricketty Street, Mascot NSW, 2020 Melbourne | 617 Spencer St, West Melbourne VIC, 3003  Get in touch with us today to discuss your next project:  🌐 www.krost.com.au  📞 1800 1KROST 📧 sales@krost.com.au  . . . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostProjects #KrostBusinessFurniture #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialFurniture #OfficeFitout #CommercialFitout #OfficeInspiration #OfficeTrends #InspirationalWorkplaces #WorkspaceTransformation','DCYYrojy7Rv','Krost','IMAGE',0),
(225,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/seating/seating-products/ted-stool','https://www.instagram.com/p/C9_2krxSwTN/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469591968_18314557090167794_8875059087578685796_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=pWSrtUjNwiUQ7kNvwHHja4j&_nc_oc=AdqsnjmBH14Rmkrj4AqGf1u8L1ZwICCa0mwe3fGc4UDhyidGoqtr7Wt05jwwBcNUixY&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQBwzy6eGvRAYricjdpEJKkLl1ihd5FpUAUCNF0c_VHz5w&oe=6A510A06','Monolite is a contemporary table range designed by Boris Berlin, defined by its distinctive thick tubular leg detail.  Inspired by monoliths and slab-like sculptures, Monolite’s design embodies simplicity as its core aesthetic principle.  Featuring locally manufactured worktops, Monolite can be customised to any size, making it ideal for a wide range of commercial settings and applications. Its design ensures exceptional structural integrity.  Visit one of our world-class showrooms and see our craftsmanship up close: Sydney | 33 Ricketty Street, Mascot NSW, 2020 Melbourne | 617 Spencer St, West Melbourne VIC, 3003  Get in touch with us today:  🌐 www.krost.com.au  📞 1800 1KROST 📧 sales@krost.com.au  Photography | @PixelCollective_Aus   . . . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostProjects #KrostBusinessFurniture #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialFurniture #CommercialDesign #InspirationalWorkplaces #FurnitureShowroom #VisitUs #CommercialFitout #AustralianDesign #OfficeFitout #QualityService #Monolite #BorisBerlin','C9_2krxSwTN','Krost','IMAGE',1),
