(237,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/storage/office-storage-products/Universal-Lockers','https://www.instagram.com/p/C5ez0NmPna9/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469549008_18314547517167794_3067878231695197562_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=105&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=5jJgWmRBuWsQ7kNvwER2igw&_nc_oc=AdqKmitl7SbD77plZmAVVZ3hm3ihrKtP97k4HSVJnIY_S9TtmkTwjrs8e8CCNAeha-s&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=RPLiYzAUeNt_Ca2YdP1m7A&oh=00_AQARhSb1EdSc_yaiDWHGzxQXTQV-VIdCKdL2NuVdHRTxQg&oe=6A507943','In the heart of Abbotsford, Plan Group has infused creativity, boundless energy, and a boost of productivity into modern, contemporary workspaces.   The Soba chair fulfils the desire for warm and tactile furniture and offers a solution that is suited to a variety of settings from reception and breakout areas to multipurpose spaces, while the Bobbi coffee table offers minimalism yet embraces a playful and modern design.  To see more of this project, visit our website linked in bio.   Designer: @plangroup_australia  Photographer: @pixelcollective_aus   .  .  . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostBusinessFurniture #KrostProjects #OfficeDesign #Architecture #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialDesign #CommercialFitout #Soba #Bobbi #UniversalLockers #Lockers #MelbourneOffice #MelbourneArchitecture','C5ez0NmPna9','Krost','IMAGE',5),
(237,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/storage/office-storage-products/Universal-Lockers','https://www.instagram.com/p/C5PoImXvR-q/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t39.30808-6/469480354_18314547373167794_5088938687851564920_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=102&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiRkVFRC5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=D4OyxvmNnxYQ7kNvwE1Eb9k&_nc_oc=Adr8mhS-A2m7-mSin8YcHshSUi08pfABqfxRpVnFYOGOMlmlWaLcefCXjk-31FLVfmg&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=RPLiYzAUeNt_Ca2YdP1m7A&oh=00_AQBhffpE4gijmQeg4ZzmtULnLsMagz1JPB8gfQuwMFA7FA&oe=6A508408','Vemi have designed an office space that balances modern business needs with design-forward thinking.  Our Benchwork workstations promote teamwork with Arc screens for privacy and clear communication. Our Arlo chairs offer a casual spot for collaboration or quiet reflection while our Universal lockers keep this open office space organised.   Designer: @vemi.au  .  .  . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostBusinessFurniture #KrostProjects #OfficeDesign #OpenOffice #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialDesign #CommercialFitout #Lockers #Collaboration','C5PoImXvR-q','Krost','IMAGE',6);
