(264,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/seating/seating-products/Miro','https://www.instagram.com/p/DJDr5PQShHb/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.75761-15/491893774_18329948665167794_2370050725356550135_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=110&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=Q1pvmTWXrckQ7kNvwFaCCSF&_nc_oc=AdplC2c5rwsGvVtwvTq-Bd2qInziQCu9YoOe-2Nez0xhNjg1du6j0tW2eNSL0WXfSFo&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQCs2h8FNdKXhMIf5IGMycVtU3ChUmikSV479aBAijPcJw&oe=6A511582','In bringing Southern Neurology’s vision to life, Nettletontribe delivered a meticulously crafted environment where sculptural joinery, technical precision, and refined aesthetics converge, creating a space that feels both considered and enduring.  🔗 Click the Project link in our bio to explore further.   #Krost #Joineryproject #Krost2025Collection #Officefurniture #KrostBusinessFurniture #furnitureshowroom #officeworkstations #officedesign #officejoinery #customjoinery','DJDr5PQShHb','Krost','IMAGE',1),
(264,'https://www.krost.com.au/products/seating/seating-products/Miro','https://www.instagram.com/p/DDWLPZ8yWDC/',NULL,'https://scontent.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656315156_18117554209654486_425630635632012261_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&_nc_cat=103&ccb=7-5&_nc_sid=18de74&efg=eyJlZmdfdGFnIjoiQ0FST1VTRUxfSVRFTS5iZXN0X2ltYWdlX3VybGdlbi5DMyJ9&_nc_ohc=rqW33o_nSOMQ7kNvwF4ECXe&_nc_oc=AdoYz0uDWvfEgR-WNh2Rn64fdp91mzAeS48sGeuD6RkrJvTLfyG0OcUJtuBqscHxJPY&_nc_zt=23&_nc_ht=scontent.cdninstagram.com&edm=AM6HXa8EAAAA&_nc_gid=E7fqpxha8g1khO1cvPMOxw&oh=00_AQA8ANrq1D--GBkrobW2Apix7Cn02Y69smwqXUOcmrHp_g&oe=6A5114F1','In collaboration with Plan Group and Grey Puksand, this contemporary fit-out creates an impressive contrast to the building’s charming historical architecture. The design infuses the workspaces with inspiration and energy, fostering productivity and innovation.  Throughout the office, our Swish Electric Height Adjustable Workstation range allows employees to work flexibly and productively in an open space. To enhance privacy and acoustic separation, our Trak Fabric Panels were added between workstations, creating a conducive environment for focused work. The team paired these workstations with our Miro Chairs, designed with forward-thinking features like automatic tension adjustment control, ensuring optimal support during long hours.  To see more of this project, visit 452 Johnston St in Krost Projects linked in bio. 🔗  Designer | @Plangroup_Australia Photographer | @PixelCollective_Aus  Visit one of our world-class showrooms: Sydney | 33 Ricketty Street, Mascot NSW, 2020 Melbourne | 617 Spencer St, West Melbourne VIC, 3003  Get in touch with us today:  🌐 www.krost.com.au  📞 1800 1KROST 📧 sales@krost.com.au  . . . . .  #Krost #KrostFurniture #KrostProjects #KrostBusinessFurniture #WorkspaceDesign #InteriorDesign #CommercialFurniture #OfficeFitout #CommercialFitout #OfficeInspiration #OfficeTrends #InspirationalWorkplaces #WorkspaceTransformation','DDWLPZ8yWDC','Kros